Zend_Service_Amazon_Ses

Incubator for development of a new Simple Email Services component.

Usage:

SendEmail:

$sendEmail = new Zend_Service_Amazon_Ses_SendEmail(
    'awskey', 'aws-secret-key'
);

$ses->addTo('to-address@domain.tld', 'Some User')
    ->setSource('from-email@example.com')
    ->setSubject('This is a message')
    ->setBody('Boom Boom Boom!!!')
    ->request();